('43419','15436','5','Renovated townhouse apartments in the heart of Palma'),
('43420','15437','5','Located in the centre of Palma, between La Rambla and Borne, this newly renovated town house disposes of 10 modern apartments. All apartments can be reached by an elevator. There are 1-3 bedroom apartments, duplex apartments (79 m² to 166 m²) and one penthouse apartment with roof terrace.\r\nThe apartments are all equipped  with kitchens from Bulthaup, hardwood floors, gas central heating, air conditioning hot / cold, sound proof windows, modern bathrooms and many more. The apartments feature double height ceilings  up to 3.5 m and will be sold unfurnished. If you are looking for an exclusive apartment in the city center of Palma you should not miss this interesting and unique opportunity. For the buyer arise 3% agency fee plus IVA on the purchase price for the acquisition of this property\r\nContact us to arrange a viewing. Plans are now available in our office.'),
